# Landing Contact Form

- **Stack**: Cloudflare Pages Function at `functions/api/leads.js`, POST `/api/leads`.
- **Destinations**: Telegram (instant notification) + Resend (email).
- **Bot**: `@multiagent_landing_bot` — token and chat ID in `cursor-context/secrets/landing.env`.

## Required env vars (Cloudflare Pages)

Set in **Workers & Pages > landing > Settings > Environment variables** (Production + Preview):

| Variable | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN` | From @BotFather |
| `TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID` | Group/channel ID where bot is added |
| `RESEND_API_KEY` | From https://resend.com/api-keys |
| `RESEND_TO_EMAIL` | Where leads are sent (e.g. lavrandge@gmail.com) |
| `RESEND_FROM_EMAIL` | Optional. Default: `MultiAgent Vision <onboarding@resend.dev>`. Use `leads@multiagent.vision` once domain DKIM is verified. |

## Domain verification (Resend)

Add the `resend._domainkey` TXT record in Cloudflare DNS for multiagent.vision. Once verified, set `RESEND_FROM_EMAIL=MultiAgent Vision <leads@multiagent.vision>`.

## Lessons learned: Web3Forms vs Resend

- **Web3Forms fails from Cloudflare Pages Functions** with error 1106 ("IP banned"). Cloudflare Workers/Pages use shared IPs; Web3Forms blocks them. No workaround from our side.
- **Resend** is the recommended solution: API key auth, no IP blocking, official Cloudflare docs. Use Resend for contact forms on Cloudflare Pages.

## Secrets location

- **cursor-context**: `secrets/landing.env` (gitignored) — canonical copy for agents.
- **Cloudflare**: Set via Dashboard or `wrangler pages secret put KEY --project-name=landing`.

## CLI: set secrets (run from `landing` repo)

Requires `wrangler login` first. Bulk upload accepts `.env` or `.dev.vars` (KEY=VALUE, no comments):

```bash
cd landing
wrangler pages secret bulk --project-name=landing --env-file=../cursor-context/secrets/landing.env
```

Or set individually:

```bash
echo "YOUR_TOKEN" | wrangler pages secret put TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN --project-name=landing
echo "-5143206875" | wrangler pages secret put TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID --project-name=landing
echo "re_xxx" | wrangler pages secret put RESEND_API_KEY --project-name=landing
echo "lavrandge@gmail.com" | wrangler pages secret put RESEND_TO_EMAIL --project-name=landing
```